text: Carrollton Public Schools is a public school district headquartered in Carrollton Township, Michigan. It is a part of the Saginaw Intermediate School District and serves the Carrollton Township area. Its schools include Carrollton Elementary School, Carrollton Middle School, and Carrollton High School. ==References== ==External links== * Carrollton Public Schools Category:School districts in Michigan Category:Saginaw Intermediate School District
